                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d245">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">793.94119/438: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Grew</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tokyo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1938-08-15T21:00:00+09:00"
                            >August 15, 1938—9 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received August 15—10:28 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>534. Department’s 285, August 12, 7 p.m.</p>
                <list>
                    <label>1.</label>
                    <item>I believe your analysis and decision to be thoroughly sound. My views have
                        not changed and they coincide with those expressed in your telegram.</item>
                    <pb facs="0266" n="262" xml:id="pg_262"/>
                    <label>2.</label>
                    <item>Last week Craigie, who is in the mountains, telephoned that he must see me
                        before his appointment with the Foreign Minister which is scheduled for
                        Wednesday, August 17. Craigie is to return to Tokyo today and I therefore
                        expect to see him tomorrow. In our conversation I shall be carefully guided
                        by your instructions.</item>
                </list>
                <p>Repeated to Hong Kong with request that Hong Kong forward code text to Ambassador
                    Johnson at Chungking by air mail.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
